seo: Nostromo webserver,远程命令执行漏洞,1.9.6,检测
summary: 该插件用于检测 Nostromo webserver <= 1.9.6 版本中的远程命令执行漏洞，通过发送特定请求验证是否存在漏洞。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect the Remote Command Execution vulnerability in Nostromo webserver <= 1.9.6 version by sending specific requests to verify the existence of the vulnerability.
